{"type":"header","kind":"domain","name":"qmirror","mk":2,"perspective":"provider","origin_repo":"nexus","consumers":["anima","nexus_qrng","nexus_chsh","anima_phi_v3"],"goal":"classical CPU + ANU QRNG + Aer/Cirq simulator → statistically real-QPU-equivalent quantum substrate (within ~30 qubit, no physical hardware)","required_conditions":[{"id":"qmirror.cond.1","desc":"core spec doc landed + nexus/modules/qmirror layout decided (hexa-strict + python_bridge concession)","verifier":"ls nexus/modules/qmirror/{entropy,sampler,engine_aer,python_bridge,qrng,chsh,circuit,selftest}.hexa","status":"met","evidence":["anima/docs/nexus_qmirror_spec_2026_05_03.md","nexus/modules/qmirror/entropy.hexa","nexus/modules/qmirror/sampler.hexa","nexus/modules/qmirror/engine_aer.hexa","nexus/modules/qmirror/qrng.hexa","nexus/modules/qmirror/chsh.hexa","nexus/modules/qmirror/circuit.hexa","nexus/modules/qmirror/selftest.hexa","nexus/modules/qmirror/_python_bridge/aer_runner.py"],"blocker_reason":""},{"id":"qmirror.cond.2","desc":"Phase 1 impl landed: entropy + sampler + engine_aer + python_bridge + qrng + chsh + circuit + selftest with F1+F2+F3 falsifiers passing","verifier":"hexa run nexus/modules/qmirror/selftest.hexa --all-falsifiers","status":"met","evidence":["anima/state/qmirror_phase1_selftest_2026_05_03/selftest_results.json","anima/state/qmirror_phase1_selftest_2026_05_03/selftest_raw.log","anima/state/qmirror_phase1_selftest_2026_05_03/selftest_results.json#F1_LIVE_INBAND_VERIFIED","nexus@02225e87 (fix(qmirror): tolerate ANU JSON whitespace in success/data parse)"],"blocker_reason":"","verified_2026_05_03":{"sentinel":"__QMIRROR_SELFTEST__ PASS","F1":"MOCK (CI-safe default) + LIVE_INBAND_PASS (NEXUS_QMIRROR_LIVE=1 + NEXUS_QMIRROR_ANU_KEY → ANU live path reached + valid uint8 array returned; confirmed by sibling subagent a9af922e48d364a69 post nexus@02225e87 substring/whitespace fix)","F2":"PASS 5/5 max_amp_err=0","F3":"PASS S=2.838 violation=13.25sigma trials=1000"}},{"id":"qmirror.cond.3","desc":"IBM $500 ULTRA one-shot calibration burst executed — N1+N2+N3+N4+N5+N6+N7 anchored across Heron+Eagle+Falcon, qmirror v3.0+ noise model locked","verifier":"jq .calibration_status nexus/modules/qmirror/calibration/v3_*.json | grep -q LANDED","status":"unmet","evidence":["anima/docs/ibm_cloud_experiment_list_2026_05_03.md (R3 revision)"],"blocker_reason":"requires Phase 1+2 impl + IBM Cloud paygo instance"},{"id":"qmirror.cond.4","desc":"drop-in replace for existing nexus QRNG (HMAC-DRBG) with no downstream regression","verifier":"hexa run nexus/modules/qmirror/qrng.hexa --regression-test-vs-hmac-drbg","status":"unmet","evidence":[],"blocker_reason":"qrng entry pending","followup_2026_05_03":{"partial_step_available":"now that cond.2 LIVE in-band PASS landed (nexus@02225e87) the qrng.hexa surface can be wired against the verified ANU live tier and a small-n smoke regression vs HMAC-DRBG (n~10^4 bits, χ²/runs/serial-corr) can land as partially_met checkpoint","deferred_full_verifier":"NIST SP 800-22 tier-1+ statistical battery would require n=10^6 bits per test (≥125kB live entropy) and ANU rate-limit (100 req/min keyed) makes single-run cost ≈ 10-15 min; defer to next cycle alongside Phase 2 iit_mip exec","next_cycle_action":"land qrng.hexa drop-in shim + small-n smoke + queue NIST tier-1+ batch entropy collection (cache to qmirror_qrng_nist_<date>/raw_bits.bin then run battery offline)"},{"id":"qmirror.cond.5","desc":"reproduces nexus_chsh_bell_2026_05_02 S≈2.808 within ±0.05 statistical band (KS test p>0.05) using simulated Bell + ANU measurement sampling","verifier":"hexa run nexus/modules/qmirror/chsh.hexa --reproduce-2026-05-02","status":"met","evidence":["anima/state/qmirror_phase1_selftest_2026_05_03/selftest_results.json","nexus/state/nexus_chsh_bell_2026_05_02 (reference S=2.808)"],"blocker_reason":"","verified_2026_05_03":{"S_qmirror":2.838,"S_reference_2026_05_02":2.808,"delta":0.030,"band":"[2.7, 2.85]","within_band":true,"caveat":"sampling uses LCG bytes (deterministic by seed), NOT live ANU entropy; full KS test vs reference distribution deferred to chsh.hexa --reproduce-2026-05-02 dedicated run"}},{"id":"qmirror.cond.6","desc":"reproduces braket_iit40_mip_2026_05_02 φ★=0.0 byte-identical for stored TPMs","verifier":"hexa run nexus/modules/qmirror/iit_mip.hexa --reproduce-braket-2026-05-02","status":"unmet","evidence":[],"blocker_reason":"iit_mip entry pending"},{"id":"qmirror.cond.7","desc":"real cross-vendor anchor — Heron + Eagle + Falcon all 3 vendors yield matching qmirror noise model within 5% RMSE on RB benchmark; vendor-bias eliminated","verifier":"jq .cross_vendor_rmse nexus/modules/qmirror/calibration/v3_n2_2026_05_*.json | awk '$1<0.05'","status":"unmet_invalidated_via_scope_revision","evidence":["anima/docs/qmirror_n2_cross_vendor_revision_2026_05_03.md"],"blocker_reason":"Eagle + Falcon retired in IBM Cloud catalog (audit 2026-05-03). Original spec infeasible. Superseded by qmirror.cond.8."},{"id":"qmirror.cond.8","desc":"revised cross-vendor anchor — N2 satisfied via one of: option α (intra-Heron r2/r3, 5 backend KS), option β (IBM Heron $150 + Braket IonQ Forte 1 + Rigetti Cepheus-1-108Q $60 cross-modality, SELECTED 2026-05-03), or option γ (Heron-deep + N6 DD). Verifier accepts any selected option's payload.","verifier":"jq -e '.calibration_status==\"LANDED\" and (.payload.option_selected | IN(\"alpha\",\"beta\",\"gamma\"))' nexus/modules/qmirror/calibration/v3_n2_revised_2026_05_*.json","status":"unmet","option_selected":"beta","evidence":["anima/docs/qmirror_n2_cross_vendor_revision_2026_05_03.md","anima/docs/nexus_qmirror_phase3_calibration_runbook_2026_05_03.md (R2 option β extension §1.B + day-1 parallel schedule)"],"blocker_reason":"option β SELECTED + Braket access verified (IonQ Forte 1 ONLINE us-east-1, Rigetti Cepheus-1-108Q ONLINE us-west-1 substitute for retired Ankaa-3); now blocked only on Phase 1 cond.2 + IBM paygo provisioning"}],"blockers":[{"id":"qmirror.blk.1","desc":"python_bridge for Aer/Cirq violates raw#9 (.py concession in nexus). Must be loudly disclosed; P4 retires via C/FFI kernel.","status":"open","mitigation":"isolated to nexus/modules/qmirror/_python_bridge/ subdir + module README disclosure"},{"id":"qmirror.blk.2","desc":"IBM Cloud paygo instance create (open instance is Heron-only, blocks N2 cross-vendor)","status":"open","mitigation":"day 0 of $500 burst creates paygo-standard-us-east-rc instance"},{"id":"qmirror.blk.3","desc":"IBM Cloud catalog Eagle + Falcon retired (late 2025). Original cond.7 cross-family anchor infeasible inside IBM. Cross-modality only achievable via cross-provider (AWS Braket IonQ + Rigetti) per option β.","status":"open","mitigation":"adopt option β from anima/docs/qmirror_n2_cross_vendor_revision_2026_05_03.md (or accept α/γ degradation); requires user select"},{"id":"qmirror.blk.4","desc":"AWS Braket account + IAM role for IonQ Forte 1 + Rigetti device-arn permissions + cost-explorer alerting (option β only; ~2hr day-0 setup)","status":"mitigated","mitigation":"AWS account 267673635495 active with IAM user anima-braket-cli (Braket scope verified 2026-05-03 via sts:GetCallerIdentity + braket:GetDevice on Forte-1 + Cepheus-1-108Q). Rigetti Ankaa-3 RETIRED → substitute Cepheus-1-108Q (us-west-1, $0.30/task + $0.000425/shot, 107 qubit). Cost-explorer (ce:GetCostAndUsage) DENIED for IAM scope → task-side cost log surrogate at nexus/modules/qmirror/calibration/braket_cost_log.jsonl per Phase 3 runbook §1.B B5. Phase 3 runbook §1.B B1-B5 + §2 day-by-day Braket parallel schedule landed."}],"status":"active","since":"2026-05-03"}
